        <mxCell id="queue_body" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=10;spacingLeft=12;spacingRight=12;" value="QMutex + two QWaitConditions (single lock serializes all cross-thread interaction)&#xa;&#xa;&#9656; submit(url, outputs, extract?, ...)  — enqueue from any thread, returns task_id (immediate)&#xa;&#9656; tryTakePending()  — GUI thread fetches pending task [NON-BLOCKING] (never blocks the event loop)&#xa;&#9656; waitForCompletion(id, timeout)  — HTTP long-poll thread blocks waiting for terminal state&#xa;&#9656; snapshot(id)  — copy result fields under lock (html/markdown/serp_json/pdf/image) for safe reads&#xa;&#9656; reportSucceeded / reportFailed  — GUI thread writes terminal state + wakes waiters" vertex="1">
